refentry.refsect1:
&ref.title.example;
The following example will add the string foo: in front of every line.
<filterchain> <prefixlines prefix="foo: " /> </filterchain>

&ref.title.attributes;


  Attributes for the <prefixlines>
  tag

  &taskAttributes.table.titlesLine.all;



    prefix

    string

    String to prepend to every line.

    &attributes.defaultValue.NA;

    &attributes.required.yes;
